					<span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-saba-gradient" data-i18n="home.hero.title2">for the AI Era</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
